# ACHIEVEMENTS REPOSITORY ATTRIBUTES
# ----------------------------------
# Standardized Git attributes for consistent rendering, text normalization,
# and structured tracking of institutional documents and certificates.

# Default text processing behavior for all tracked items
* text=auto eol=lf

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Text and Documentation
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Explicitly identify text-based formats for consistent line ending application
*.md text diff
*.txt text diff
*.csv text diff
*.json text diff

# Classify markdown files as documentation for repository metrics
*.md linguist-documentation

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Binary Credentials and Media Storage
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Protect binary assets from text normalization and corruption.
# This repository primarily warehouses scanned certificates and visual evidence.
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Archive Formats
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevent corruption of archived credentials
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
*.gz binary
*.rar binary
*.7z binary
